name: Possessed Awakening
desc: All monsters you control gain 300 ATK for each different Attribute among monsters you control. “Charmer” and “Familiar-Possessed” monsters you control cannot be destroyed by card effects. If a Spellcaster monster whose original ATK is 1850 is Normal or Special Summoned to your field: Draw 1 card. You can only use this effect of “Possessed Awakening” once per turn.
